001package com.technototes.library.util;
002
003import android.util.Pair;
004import java.util.HashMap;
005import java.util.Map;
006
007public class MapUtils {
008
009    @SafeVarargs
010    public static <T, U> Map<T, U> of(Pair<T, U>... entries) {
011        Map<T, U> map = new HashMap<>();
012        for (Pair<T, U> e : entries) {
013            map.put(e.first, e.second);
014        }
015        return map;
016    }
017}
